"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-coco-gauff-team-usa-flag-bearer-with-lebron-james-paris-games\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tennis star Coco Gauff was left speechless upon finding out she would be the female flag bearer for the United States at the Paris Olympics opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12, \"end\": 22, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}, {\"begin\": 104, \"end\": 117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999981024602489, \"rank\": 7.474796577914783e-07, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gauff\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s compatriot and longtime friend, Christopher Eubanks, surprised her with the news on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 159, \"to\": 263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 201, \"end\": 220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christopher_Eubanks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Christopher Eubanks\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christopher_Eubanks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christopher_Eubanks\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYour year last year was incredible,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Eubanks said.\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou captured the world by storm.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You captured your first Grand Slam.\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 392, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think you kind of showcased to the world, in the U.S. and abroad, how special of a person and tennis player you are.\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think because you are so special, you have the honor of wearing this jacket during the opening ceremony and being a flag bearer with LeBron James.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Gauff\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s mouth dropped to the floor.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI was not expecting that,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Gauff said as she gave Eubanks a heartfelt hug.\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThank you, that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s really cool.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Opening Ceremony Flag Bearer@CocoGauff.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ba\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b8The moment Coco got the news from her teammate@chris_eubanks96\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00ab\\u00a2#ParisOlympicspic.twitter.com/yjIWPjm6J1  Gauff, 20, will be the youngest ever U.S. flag bearer at an Olympic opening ceremony and the first tennis player to be bestowed the honor.\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1025, \"end\": 1034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999995829967, \"rank\": 4.1698799803058957e-10, \"text\": \"U.S. flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gauff is currently ranked as the world No.\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2 by the WTA and is coming off a Grand Slam title in 2023.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_Tennis_Association\", \"score\": 0.9998070083049486, \"rank\": 0.00018501677893362556, \"text\": \"WTA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"